{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we stayed there, I know for sure, it was two nights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I don't believe it was further than two nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And it-- always outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We never had the chance to go inside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Never had a shelter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Never heard, anybody, any question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And from that day on, although we heard previously rumors, but from that day on, that rumor, life and live by the rumor was extremely high.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rumor was basically, that they are assembling people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Jews, being arrested, that we are going to go and go to some kind of labor camp, or somehow, somewhere, to work towards the betterment of the war, for the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- you know, like-- I-- I-- it's very difficult to describe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the-- the major support was my brother who was, at that time, already almost 18.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was strong and continuously telling and explaining that you have to do anything, whatsoever, to be strong and support and-- and-- and supportive of each other, number one.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And try to do anything possible to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing, what we tried at that time-- well, naturally we couldn't achieve anything at least, not at the beginning, to let mom and dad know that we are alive, where we are.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they knew only one thing, that we left for school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by the first afternoon, they knew that we are not back anywhere where we're supposed to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no such a thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on we found the gendarme who was willing to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we promised to that Hungarian gendarme if he delivers the message to-- to them, call-- to call them on the telephone he's going to receive like, let's translate it, $100.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
